data.description: This charming 3 bd, 2 ba home is located on a corner lot, centrally located for easy access to shopping, dining and schools! Beautifully updated with recent paint, granite countertops & vinyl flooring! There is also a versatile bonus room with endless possibilities! Recent improvements include gutter installation, LED lights, fans, windows, blinds, gutters and an auto sprinkler system. Don't miss the RV covered parking pad! This home is both stylish and functional. Ring security system conveys.
